snippet: The weather pattern over the Pacific had been expected, but it is described as so weak that it is not likely to bring much-needed rain to California.
abstract: Government scientists report formation of long-anticipated El Nino pattern in the Pacific Ocean, but note that it will likely have little impact on weather worldwide.
lead_paragraph: The weather pattern over the Pacific had been expected, but it is described as so weak that it is not likely to bring much-needed rain to California.

headline.main: El Niño Forms, but Forecasters See Little Weather Impact
